		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Dice 10000</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Farkle_dice.jpg" class="image" title="a family dice game"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ee/Farkle_dice.jpg/250px-Farkle_dice.jpg" width="250" height="188" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Farkle_dice.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
a family dice game</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>6-Dice</b>, <b>10,000 Dice</b> (or "Dice_10000") is the name of a family dice game, very similar to <a href="/wiki/Farkle" title="Farkle">Farkle</a>. It also goes by other names, including Zilch, Foo, Boxcar, and Crap Out.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
